org.jlab.coda.emu.support.codaComponent

Interface CODAStateMachine

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    DataChannel, DataTransport, EmuModule
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CODAStateMachineAdapter, DataChannelAdapter, DataChannelImplCmsg, DataChannelImplEmu, DataChannelImplEt, DataChannelImplFifo, DataChannelImplFile, DataTransportAdapter, DataTransportImplCmsg, DataTransportImplEmu, DataTransportImplEt, DataTransportImplFifo, DataTransportImplFile, Dummy, EventRecording, FarmController, FastEventBuilder, ModuleAdapter, RocFixedRateSimulation, RocSimulation, TsFixedRateSimulation, TsSimulation

    public interface CODAStateMachine
    This interface is used when defining data transports, data channels, and modules. It encompasses all state machine functions and the ability to notify others of an END event's arrival.
    Author:
    timmer Date: 4/18/13
    See Also:
    CODATransition
